{"type":"assistant","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Phase 4 Track B (SMTP mailboxes + single send) is implemented. Summary:\n\n## Delivered\n\n**Schema & migration**\n- `mailbox` and `message` tables in `packages/db/src/schema/mail.ts`\n- Migration `0002_phase4_mailbox_message.sql` with indexes and a minimal `prospect` stub + FK for isolated worktree dev\n\n**Mail package**\n- SMTP adapter (`createSmtpAdapter`, `sendMime` with raw MIME + envelope)\n- AES-256-GCM credential encryption (`crypto.ts`)\n- DNS auth checker for SPF/DKIM/DMARC (`dns.ts`)\n- Unit tests for all three\n\n**Server functions**\n- `mailboxes.functions.ts` — CRUD, health check, test send (credentials never returned to client)\n- `compose.functions.ts` — prospect search + `sendComposedMessage` with compliance/threading\n\n**UI routes**\n- `/settings/mailboxes` — list, health dots, test send, delete\n- `/settings/mailboxes/new` — SMTP connect form (Gmail/Microsoft disabled for Wave 2)\n- `/compose` — mailbox picker, prospect typeahead, send with follow-up sequence stub link\n\n## Verification\n\n- `pnpm check` — **green** (60 tests)\n- Mailpit smoke — send succeeded with normalized Message-Id, `List-Unsubscribe`, and physical-address footer\n\n## Notes\n\n- `sendMime()` needs an explicit SMTP `envelope` when using `raw` MIME (nodemailer requirement)\n- Tenancy guard now matches `tables.<name>` only to avoid false positives on the word “message”\n- DKIM is DNS presence only; full key validation is deferred to R-044 Wave 2\n- Unsubscribe URL is a Phase 10 placeholder: `https://app.example.com/u/pending`\n\n`RESULT.json` is at the worktree root. Ensure `.env` has `MAILBOX_ENCRYPTION_KEY` (32-byte base64) before creating SMTP mailboxes in the UI."}]},"session_id":"96149331-134f-48b3-9ea0-fe7607af1532"}
